OL,3,COfficers at Windsor Castle
OL,4,Cinvestigated over allegations of
OL,5,Csleeping on duty
OL,7,FPolice officers protecting the royal
OL,8,Ffamily at Windsor Castle are under
OL,9,Finvestigation over allegations they
OL,10,Fslept while on duty.
OL,12,FA number of officers on protective
OL,13,Fduties from the Metropolitan Police's
OL,14,FRoyalty and Specialist Protection team
OL,15,Fare being investigated after concerns
OL,16,Fwere raised.
OL,18,FAllegations include officers leaving
OL,19,Fposts unattended and sleeping while on
OL,20,Fduty.
