CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779095182
OL,3,COfficers at Windsor Castle
OL,4,Cinvestigated over allegations of
OL,5,Csleeping on duty
OL,7,FThe Met's Directorate of Professional
OL,8,FStandards (DPS) has launched an
OL,9,Finvestigation and the Independent
OL,10,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC) has
OL,11,Fbeen informed, the force said.
OL,13,FA decision from the DPS over whether
OL,14,Fany of the officers under
OL,15,Finvestigation should be placed on
OL,16,Frestrictive duties is expected before
OL,17,Fthe end of next week.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
