PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779095182
OL,3,COfficers at Windsor Castle
OL,4,Cinvestigated over allegations of
OL,5,Csleeping on duty
OL,7,FA Met Police spokesperson said: "The
OL,8,FMet's Directorate of Professional
OL,9,FStandards has launched an urgent
OL,10,Finvestigation following concerns
OL,11,Fraised regarding the conduct of a
OL,12,Fnumber of officers on protective
OL,13,Fduties at Windsor Castle.
OL,15,F"The allegations include officers
OL,16,Fleaving posts unattended and sleeping
OL,17,Fwhile on duty.
OL,26,@oD@aOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
