PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779095182
OL,3,COfficers at Windsor Castle
OL,4,Cinvestigated over allegations of
OL,5,Csleeping on duty
OL,7,F"The alleged behaviour falls below the
OL,8,Fhigh standards expected of officers,
OL,9,Fparticularly in frontline protective
OL,10,Froles.
OL,12,F"The Independent Office for Police
OL,13,FConduct has been informed and
OL,14,Fconcluded that this matter will be
OL,15,Finvestigated locally by the Met.
OL,17,F"As part of their inquiries, DPS is
OL,18,Fassessing whether any of those under
OL,19,Finvestigation should be placed on
OL,20,Frestricted duties.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
