CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779095182
OL,3,COfficers at Windsor Castle
OL,4,Cinvestigated over allegations of
OL,5,Csleeping on duty
OL,7,F"A decision is expected to be made on
OL,8,Fthis before the end of next week."
OL,10,FBuckingham Palace declined to comment
OL,11,Fand the IOPC was unavailable to
OL,12,Fcomment.
